18#include <cmath>
19
20namespace ZXing {
21
22template <typename T>
23struct PointT
24{
25 using value_t = T;
26 T x = 0, y = 0;
27
28 PointT() = default;
29 PointT(T x, T y) : x(x), y(y) {}
30
31 template <typename U>
32 explicit PointT(const PointT<U>& p) : x(static_cast<T>(p.x)), y(static_cast<T>(p.y))
33 {}
34};
35
36template <typename T>
37bool operator==(const PointT<T>& a, const PointT<T>& b)
38{
39 return a.x == b.x && a.y == b.y;
40}
41
42template <typename T>
43bool operator!=(const PointT<T>& a, const PointT<T>& b)
44{
45 return !(a == b);
46}
47
48template <typename T, typename U>
49auto operator+(const PointT<T>& a, const PointT<U>& b) -> PointT<decltype(a.x + b.x)>
50{
51 return {a.x + b.x, a.y + b.y};
52}
53
54template <typename T, typename U>
55auto operator-(const PointT<T>& a, const PointT<U>& b) -> PointT<decltype(a.x - b.x)>
56{
57 return {a.x - b.x, a.y - b.y};
58}
59
60template <typename T, typename U>
61PointT<T> operator*(U s, const PointT<T>& a)
62{
63 return {s * a.x, s * a.y};
64}
65
66template <typename T, typename U>
67PointT<T> operator/(const PointT<T>& a, U d)
68{
69 return {a.x / d, a.y / d};
70}
71
72template <typename T, typename U>
73double operator*(const PointT<T>& a, const PointT<U>& b)
74{
75 return double(a.x) * b.x + a.y * b.y;
76}
77
78template <typename T>
79double distance(PointT<T> a, PointT<T> b)
80{
81 auto d = a - b;
82 return std::sqrt(d * d);
83}
84
85template <typename T>
86double crossProduct(PointT<T> a, PointT<T> b)
87{
88 return a.x * b.y - b.x * a.y;
89}
90
91using PointI = PointT<int>;
92using PointF = PointT<double>;
93
94template <typename T>
95PointF normalized(PointT<T> a)
96{
97 return PointF(a) / distance(a, {});
98}
99
100inline PointI round(PointF p)
101{
102 return PointI(::lround(p.x), ::lround(p.y));
103}
104
105} // ZXing
